<div class="container">
    <div class="row pt-2">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card border-primary mb-3">
          <div class="card-body text-dark">
            <h4 class="card-title"><%= @goal.name %></h4>
            <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">Goal</h6>
            <dl class="row">
              <dt class="col-sm-5">Deadline:</dt>
              <dd class="col-sm-7"><%= @goal.deadline.strftime("%d %b %Y") if @goal.deadline %></dd>

              <dt class="col-sm-5">Is this goal achievable?</dt>
              <dd class="col-sm-7"><%= @goal.achievability.humanize %></dd>

              <dt class="col-sm-5">How will you know if you succeeded?</dt>
              <dd class="col-sm-7"><%= @goal.measurement ? @goal.measurement : "Not with a ruler ¯\\_(ツ)_/¯ " %></dd>

              <dt class="col-sm-5">Who is reponsible?</dt>
              <dd class="col-sm-7"><%= @goal.person_responsible ? @goal.person_responsible : "Most probably me (Ͼ˳Ͽ)..!!! "%></dd>

              <dt class="col-sm-5">Was this goal achieved?</dt>
              <dd class="col-sm-7"><%= @goal.achieved.humanize %></dd>

              <dt class="col-sm-5">Date completed:</dt>
              <dd class="col-sm-7"><%= @goal.completed_at ? @goal.completed_at.strftime("%d %b %Y") : "Working on it... (-.-)Zzz..."  %></dd>
            </dl>
          </div>
          <div class="card-footer">
            <%= link_to 'Back', polymorphic_path([@goalable, Goal]), class: "card-link"  %>&nbsp;
            <%= link_to 'Edit', edit_polymorphic_path([@goalable, @goal]), class: "card-link" %>&nbsp;
            <%= link_to "Add a comment", "#", class: "card-link" %>
            <%= link_to "Add action plans", "#", class: "card-link" %>
          </div>
        </div> <!-- .card -->
      </div><!-- .col -->
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card border-info">
          <div class="card-header">
            To do list and Action Plans
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <p class="card-text">
              Step 1: Brainstorm a “To Do” list. Write down
              everything you must do in order to achieve this goal.
            </p>
            <p class="card-link">
              Step 2: Now turn this “To Do” list into an “Action Plan”.
              Prioritise the list. Number the items on the list in the order you must do them,
              according to: (a) their importance and (b) the time needed to complete the task.
            </p>
          </div>
          <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
            <li class="list-group-item">Cras justo odio</li>
            <li class="list-group-item">Dapibus ac facilisis in</li>
            <li class="list-group-item">Vestibulum at eros</li>
          </ul>
        </div><!-- .card -->
      </div><!-- .col -->
  </div><!-- .row -->
</div><!-- .container-->
